Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari, you really never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's {\i1}that{\i0} mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say \NI haven't changed at all?
